paycheck to housing (then bills...then food...then everything else).

I love Vermin Supreme, but I actually think Jimmy McMillan has a platform 
that could get him elected.

I know they have each other as their respective VP's...but either way it's 
time to get these two-party clowns out of your government.  As much as I 
wish we would do it, Aussies are way too laid back to get shit done...and 
we only get "hung parliaments" when both majors really fuck up so badly 
that everyone "protest votes".

On the other hand, I think the people of the US could pull of a bloodless 
3rd party/independent coup!﻿
